title: Platinum LEED certification, Stainless Appliances, Washer/Dryer
posting_body: ['Venice on Rose', 'Welcome to Venice on Rose.', 'Here you will find thoughtfully designed one- and two-bedroom Venice apartment homes that offer you a whole new world of upscale living.', 'All of our apartment homes boast features like a gas range stovetop with hood, recycled-content flooring, patios or balconies, courtyard, high ceilings and walk-in closets.', 'Discover amazing facilities within reach, such as a resident herb garden, bike storage, and secure parking.', 'Your new home awaits you here at Venice on Rose.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 48', 'OR Text', '48', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Follow The Link', 'Below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1317 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Gas Cooking', '- Walk-in Closets* in select units', '- Patio/Balcony', '- Fully - Equipped Kitchen', '- Stainless Appliances', '- Hard Surface Flooring', '- Washer/Dryer', 'Community Amenities', '- Parking', '- Fitness Center', '- Platinum LEED certification', '- Pet Friendly - on-site dog run', '- On-Site Retail', '- Bike Storage', 'Pet Policy', 'We love our four legged friends here!', 'Both cats and dogs accepted', 'Maximum of two pets per apartment home', 'Breed restrictions apply', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Venice on Rose', '512 Rose Avenue, Venice, CA, 90291', 'Greystar California, Inc., Broker License #01525765', 'DMCA Agent: <URL>', 'Ad0JU0KgmB']
